<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="pow" id="pow">pow</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Sintaxis:

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">pow</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> base, <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

La función pow() devuelve <em>base</em> elevado a la potencia <em>exp</em>. 
</p>

<p>
Un error de dominio es devuelto si:

</p>
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <em>base</em> es cero y <em>exp</em> es menor o igual que cero</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <em>base</em> es negativa y <em>exp</em> no es un número entero</div>
</li>
</ul>

<p>

Un error de rango es devuelto si hay desbordamiento.
</p>

<p>
C++ proporciona las siguientes formas de sobrecarga:

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">float</span> <span class="kw3">pow</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">float</span> base, <span class="kw4">float</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span> <span class="co1">// igual que powf() en C99</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">pow</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> base, <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span> <span class="co1">// igual que powl() en C99</span></pre>
<p>
Además, C++ proporciona las versiones de pow() con exponenciación entera:

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">float</span> <span class="kw3">pow</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">float</span> base, <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">pow</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> base, <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">pow</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> base, <span class="kw4">int</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
